data.description: OWNER WILL FINANCE.. Welcome to this mid century modern beauty. You will love all the large rooms and great storage space throughout.  All three bathrooms have been completely updated. The primary bedroom has a great sitting area that would make the perfect office. The upstairs loft is huge and even has a full bath and its own private balcony.  The backyard is an oasis with a large deck. The large living dining area is a great place to entertain. STORM SHELTER in the garage.  Don't miss this one. Buyer to verify all info including schools. Seller has an active Real Estate License washer, dryer fridge stay with property. Seller would condider owner finance call about terms.
